15 Department of Corrections, or employee of a private prison
16 contractor was acting within the scope of their his or her
17 employment. No earned credit deductions shall be credited or
18 recorded for any person who is referred to an intermediate
19 revocation facility for violating any of the terms and conditions of
20 probation.
